#sample-tooltips
  h4 Tooltips

  p.align-justify.
    Tooltips are an important part of UX, where you can give user additional information about
    a component  placed on his/her screen. <code class="primary">Seed-css</code> gives you a
    simple but very efficient tooltip, which doesn't even need javascript.

  .tooltips
    .grid
      .row
        .col.md-3
          p.with-tooltip.show.align-center
           span A
           span.tooltip.top Top tooltip
        .col.md-3
          p.with-tooltip.show.align-center
           span A
           span.tooltip.right Right tooltip
        .col.md-3
          p.with-tooltip.show.align-center
           span A
           span.tooltip Bottom tooltip
        .col.md-3
          p.with-tooltip.show.align-center
           span A
           span.tooltip.left Left tooltip

  br

  .code-sample
    pre.prettyprint.lang-html.
      &lt;!-- top --&gt;
      &lt;div class="with-tooltip" &gt;
        ...
        &lt;span class="tooltip top" &gt; ...  &lt;/span&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;

      &lt;!-- right --&gt;
      &lt;div class="with-tooltip" &gt;
        ...
        &lt;span class="tooltip right" &gt; ...  &lt;/span&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;

      &lt;!-- bottom (default) --&gt;
      &lt;div class="with-tooltip" &gt;
        ...
        &lt;span class="tooltip" &gt; ...  &lt;/span&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;

      &lt;!-- left --&gt;
      &lt;div class="with-tooltip" &gt;
        ...
        &lt;span class="tooltip left" &gt; ...  &lt;/span&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;
